c: 29
v: 33
t: "Phir jab hamare faristade (emissaries/messengers) Lut ke paas pahunchey to unki aamad par woh sakht pareshan aur dil tangg hua. Unhon ne kaha “ na daro aur na ranjh karo, hum tumhein aur tumhare ghar walon ko bacha lenge, siwaye tumhari biwi ke jo peechey reh janey walon mein se hai"